### App-8: User profile setup
**Current state:** Implemented in v0.4. Name, DOB, conditions, doctor info, photo. Used for greetings and PDF report.

**Open follow-ups:**
- Multi-user profile support (one phone managing multiple wearers — partial scaffolding in v0.3)
- Photo storage size limits and resizing
- Conditions list — should we expand beyond diabetes to include hypertension, atrial fibrillation, COPD, etc.? Each adds metric prominence logic.

**Priority:** Medium. Iterate as users surface needs.

